 be a\nmirage, since parameters yielding higher EW scales would be in the swampland\nand would not count as possible consistent theories. This would bring a new\nperspective into the issue of the EW hierarchy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2017 18:06:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Aug 2017 22:03:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-06"}
