 affected by a quasi-resonance with Mimas,\nwhich induces long-term orbital oscillations of its eccentricity and\ninclination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2017 18:07:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
