ode-changing phenomena which occurs on a global magnetospheric scale, (4)\nGeometric reasons are less favoured as a likely cause of nulling phenomena due\nto the randomness and broadband behaviour reported in this thesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2017 19:03:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-20"}
