nand their time evolution could be compared with the observed characteristics of\nmerger shocks, constraining interpretations of relevant observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Jun 2017 10:02:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Feb 2018 09:21:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-25"}
